Organization: <%= resource.name.black.bold %>

<%= "ID: #{ resource._id }, external_id: #{ resource.external_id }, url: #{ resource.url }".light_blue %>

Properties:
-----------

Domain names: <%= resource.domain_names.join(", ") %>
Detail: <%= resource.details %>
Shared Tickets: <%= colorize_boolean(resource.shared_tickets) %>


Meta:
-----

Created at: <%= resource.created_at.to_s %>
Tags:  <%= resource.tags.join(", ") %>


Users:
------<% if resource.users.empty? %>
The organization does not have any users
<% else %>
<% resource.users.each do |user| %>
- Name: <%= user.name %>, Email: <%= user.email %>, ID: <%= user._id %>
<% end %><% end %>

Tickets:
------<% if resource.tickets.empty? %>
The organization does not have any tickets
<% else %>
<% resource.tickets.each do |ticket| %>
- Subject: <%= ticket.subject %>, ID: <%= ticket._id %>
<% end %><% end %>

<%= ("-" * 100).black.bold %>
